Package sngforge.java2r

Class Summary
RBase This class forms the basic port to the R executable.
RFactory This class should be initialized at the start of the program.
RGraphics This class provides an interface to perform graphical operations with R.
RHelp This class can be used for displaying the help from R.
RParser This class parses R commands by converting them to a script.
The command to be executed can be passed as a String and multiple lines can be entered by using the newline character.
RScript This class parses R scipts stored in a file.
After the execution the proc.time() command is executed automatically.
 

Exception Summary
RException Exception due to miscellaneous error.
RFactoryException Exception due to error in initialization of RFactory
